title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (August 14 - September 10) will also receive:

— The Pegassi Torero XO (Super)
— 50% off Auto Shop Properties
— The Atomic Racing Bomber Zipped and Atomic Racing Cap
— 2X Rewards on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales
— 50% off Drift Tuning Upgrades
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
